data.name: SqlCommand1.CommandText
data.value:
SELECT DISTINCT Siparis.SiparisID, Siparis.SipEvrakSeri, Siparis.SipEvrakSira, Siparis.CariKod, Siparis.CariUnvan, Siparis.Onayli, Siparis.Onaylayan, Siparis.Iptal, SipDetay.BolumKod, SipDetay.KategoriID, Kategoriler.KategoriKod, Kategoriler.KategoriIsim, SipDetay.Miktar, SipDetay.TerminTarihi, SipDetay.MusteriSipNo, SipDetay.Bedenler, Okullar.OkulKod, SipDetay.Tarih, Siparis.SipEvrakSeri + '-' + CASE WHEN LEN(CAST(Siparis.SipEvrakSira AS VARCHAR(10)))<5 THEN REPLACE( SPACE(5-LEN(CAST(Siparis.SipEvrakSira AS VARCHAR(10)))) ,' ' ,'0') ELSE '' END + CAST(Siparis.SipEvrakSira AS VARCHAR(10)) AS SiparisNo, SipDetay.SipDetayID
,Siparis.OdemeDurumu,Siparis.Odenen,CASE Siparis.SiparisType WHEN 0 THEN 'Müşteri' ELSE 'Depo Siparişi' END as sSiparisType , SipDetay.AnaRenk , SipDetay.Durumu , SipDetay.BoyahaneID, Siparis.SiparisAlanID, SipDetay.Iskonto,SipDetay.NakitIskonto,SipDetay.IskontoTutar,SipDetay.NakitIskontoTutar, ROUND(SipDetay.Fiyat * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END,2) as Fiyat , SipDetay.Tutar * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END as Tutar , Siparis.VadeFarkiOran , ROUND((Siparis.VadeFarkiOran/100) * SipDetay.Tutar * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END,2) as VadeFarkiTutar , Siparis.KdvOran , ROUND((Siparis.KdvOran/100) * ((1+Siparis.VadeFarkiOran/100) * SipDetay.Tutar) * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END,2) as KdvTutari , ROUND( (1+ Siparis.KdvOran/100) * ((1+Siparis.VadeFarkiOran/100) * SipDetay.Tutar) * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END,2) as ToplamTutar ,Siparis.DovizTipi, CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN NULL WHEN 1 THEN NULL ELSE SipDetay.Tutar END as DovizTutar , CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END as DovizKuru
,SipDetay.TeslimMiktar , SipDetay.Miktar-SipDetay.TeslimMiktar as Kalan, CASE WHEN SipDetay.Durumu='BITTI' THEN 'TESLIM EDILMIS' ELSE CASE WHEN SipDetay.TeslimMiktar<=0 THEN 'YOK' WHEN SipDetay.Miktar>SipDetay.TeslimMiktar THEN 'KISMI' WHEN SipDetay.Miktar<=SipDetay.TeslimMiktar THEN 'TESLIM EDILMIS' ELSE '' END END as SevkDurumu ,svk.IlkSevkTarihi ,svk.IlkSevkEvrakNo ,svk.SonSevkTarihi ,svk.SonSevkEvrakNo ,svk.SevkAdet , ROUND(svk.SevkAdet * SipDetay.Fiyat * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END ,2) as SevkTutar , ROUND((Siparis.VadeFarkiOran/100) * (svk.SevkAdet * SipDetay.Fiyat) * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END,2) as SevkVadeFarkiTutar , ROUND((Siparis.KdvOran/100) * (svk.SevkAdet * SipDetay.Fiyat) * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END,2) as SevkKdvTutar ,ROUND( (1 + Siparis.VadeFarkiOran/100 + Siparis.KdvOran/100) * (svk.SevkAdet * SipDetay.Fiyat) * CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE Siparis.DovizKuru END ,2) as SevkToplamTutar ,CASE Siparis.DovizKuru WHEN 0 THEN NULL WHEN 1 THEN NULL ELSE CASE ISNULL(SipDetay.Miktar,0) WHEN 0 THEN 0 ELSE ROUND(Siparis.GenelToplam * svk.SevkAdet/SipDetay.Miktar,2) END END as SevkDovizTutar
, SipDetay.FasondaMi , Okullar.OkulIsmi + ' / ' + ISNULL(Ilce.IlceIsmi, '') + ' - ' + ISNULL(Il.IlIsmi, '') AS OkulIsmi, Okullar.IlceID, Okullar.IlID, Il.IlIsmi, Ilce.IlceIsmi ,SipDetayRenkler.R002_Lastik ,SipDetayRenkler.R002_LastikCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R003_Yaka ,SipDetayRenkler.R003_YakaCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R004_DubleLastikCep ,SipDetayRenkler.R004_DubleLastikCepCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R005_DubleLastikPilotYaka ,SipDetayRenkler.R005_DubleLastikPilotYakaCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R006_DubleLastik ,SipDetayRenkler.R006_DubleLastikCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R007_DubleYaka ,SipDetayRenkler.R007_DubleYakaCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R008_TorbaliBant ,SipDetayRenkler.R008_TorbaliBantCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R012_LakosYaka ,SipDetayRenkler.R012_LakosYakaCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R013_Manset2cm ,SipDetayRenkler.R013_Manset2cmCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R014_Manset6cm ,SipDetayRenkler.R014_Manset6cmCizgiler ,SipDetayRenkler.R018_EtekManseti ,SipDetayRenkler.R018_EtekMansetiCizgiler , Saticilar.SaticiIsmi
,SipDetay.CreatedBy, SipDetay.CreatedDate, SipDetay.ModifiedBy, SipDetay.ModifiedDate FROM SipDetay WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN Okullar WITH (NOLOCK) ON SipDetay.OkulID = Okullar.OkulID INNER JOIN Siparis WITH (NOLOCK) ON SipDetay.SiparisID = Siparis.SiparisID INNER JOIN Kategoriler WITH (NOLOCK) ON SipDetay.KategoriID = Kategoriler.KategoriID LEFT OUTER JOIN Ilce WITH (NOLOCK) ON Okullar.IlceID = Ilce.IlceID LEFT OUTER JOIN Il WITH (NOLOCK) ON Okullar.IlID = Il.IlID LEFT OUTER JOIN SipDetayRenkler WITH (NOLOCK) ON SipDetay.SipDetayID = SipDetayRenkler.SipDetayID LEFT OUTER JOIN Saticilar WITH (NOLOCK) ON Siparis.SaticiID = Saticilar.SaticiID LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT SevkDetay.SipDetayID, MIN(Sevk.Tarih) as IlkSevkTarihi, MAX(Sevk.Tarih) as SonSevkTarihi,SUM(SevkDetay.Adet) as SevkAdet, MIN(Sevk.SevkEvrakSeri + '-' + CAST(Sevk.SevkEvrakSira as VARCHAR(20))) as IlkSevkEvrakNo, MAX(Sevk.SevkEvrakSeri + '-' + CAST(Sevk.SevkEvrakSira as VARCHAR(20))) as SonSevkEvrakNo
FROM SevkDetay WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN Sevk WITH (NOLOCK) ON Sevk.SevkID = SevkDetay.SevkID WHERE Sevk.Deleted=0 AND Sevk.Iptal=0 AND SevkDetay.Deleted=0 GROUP BY SevkDetay.SipDetayID ) svk ON svk.SipDetayID = SipDetay.SipDetayID WHERE (SipDetay.Deleted = 0) AND (Siparis.Iptal = 0) AND Siparis.Deleted = 0
